title: FiveWire Music
description: Search songs, create playlists, and view trending songs! You must have a Spotify account to access FiveWire. If you haven't made a FiveWire account, use the guest username:  and password:

title: SmartTrvl
description: Enter your flight origin and destination, and your budget. You'll be given flights within your price range, and COVID statistics for the given country.

title: Eat-Da-Burger
description: Enter a burger that sounds delicious, which will append that burger to the screen. Then, devour the burger with the Devour button, marking the burger as devoured. Click the Delete button to get rid of your burger.

title: Employee Tracker
description: This command-line application allows the user to manage employees, departments, job roles, and employee managers in a database through viewing, adding, updating, and deleting entries.

title: Note Taker
description: Write notes and save them for later! Then, delete any notes when finished with them.

title: Workout Tracker
description: Create a new workout with different exercises. Document your exercises each day, and view your workout stats and total durations on the dashboard page.
